  <description>
    <narrative>Funding for Save the Children for Community Based Disaster Risk Reduction (DRR) and Climate Change Adaptation (CCA) in Oodweyne, Somaliland and supporting the ‘Enabling Children’s Action on Disasters’ project (ECAD) for DRR and CCA education in Kenya. This DRR focus will introduce medium and long term development planning for livelihood adaption in arid zones to complement short term emergency relief interventions already underway. The total value of this initiative is $1.2 million over 2 years, starting 2010-11.</narrative>
